Package: x3ptools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for working with x3p files
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2018-02-05
Authors@R: c(person("Heike", "Hofmann", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                      email = "hofmann@iastate.edu"), 
             person("Ganesh", "Krishnan", role = c("ctb"),
                      email = "ganeshk@iastate.edu"))
Author: Heike Hofmann [aut, cre], Ganesh Krishnan, CSAFE
Maintainer: Heike Hofmann <hofmann@iastate.edu>
Description: x3p files are specified in ISO standard 5436:2000 for 3d surface measurements. `x3ptools` allows reading, writing and basic modifications to these objects.
Depends: R (>= 3.3),
         digest (>= 0.6.15),
         xml2 (>= 1.2.0),
         rgl (>= 0.98.1),
